15:40.348 --> 15:42.290
I might say, hey, can I take your coat?

15:42.466 --> 15:43.207
Hey, come on in.

15:43.227 --> 15:44.108
You could come to the kitchen.

15:44.548 --> 15:46.350
Can I get you a drink?

15:46.370 --> 15:48.533
If we're really close, I said, help yourself to anything.

15:48.933 --> 15:49.854
My house is your house.

15:50.495 --> 15:53.818
We even had this red plate that I think maybe Stephen made years ago.

15:54.159 --> 15:56.021
It was called the special plate.

15:56.041 --> 15:59.484
And if you're really special and you came to our house, you got the special plate.

