16:01.547 --> 16:02.948
Now you just get the regular plate.

16:02.968 --> 16:05.431
But in our heart, you still get the special plate.

16:05.471 --> 16:06.172
There's just customs.

16:06.192 --> 16:07.333
Well, this was the way it was.

16:07.673 --> 16:12.018
