16:18.326 --> 16:22.813
And you would greet someone with a kiss on the face and say, you're welcome, you're loved here.

16:23.053 --> 16:27.640
And you might even anoint their head with oil saying, you're an honored guest in our home.

16:28.541 --> 16:31.205
