19:27.640 --> 19:29.723
She was in awe that she got to be in his presence.

19:30.604 --> 19:32.466
She took probably her most valuable

19:32.578 --> 19:38.147
possession and gave it to him as a sacrificial act of worship to say, I need your grace and your love.

19:38.187 --> 19:40.610
You're honored in my presence.

19:43.054 --> 19:44.997
They treated him as common.

19:47.641 --> 19:48.663
She treated him as holy.

19:50.486 --> 19:54.352
The Pharisees were comfortable with his presence.

19:56.395 --> 19:58.578
She was overwhelmed by him.

20:13.154 --> 20:17.123
For some of you, this is your story.

20:19.147 --> 20:23.878
If you look back to last year, not what you believe, but what your life says you believe.

20:25.642 --> 20:27.125
You didn't walk away from God.

20:27.145 --> 20:33.138
You just grew comfortable with them.

20:42.018 --> 20:43.179
I've seen it at some of you.

20:45.001 --> 20:46.983
If you've been here long enough, you've seen it knee at times.

20:49.566 --> 20:52.989
Some of you, I mean, you used to worship with awe.

